3. Get DIABLO 2: LORD OF DESTRUCTION v1.11b [ENGLISH] NO-CD/FIXED EXE (1.05MB) from here ( http://www.gameburnworld.com/gp/gamefixes/diablo2lordofdestruction.shtml )

4. Extract the rar, and you will get a file that is 2.03 MB large, named simply "Game".

5. Back up the existing "Game" file, located in your Diablo 2 directory, then replace it with the crack.

Congratulations, you now have a cracked version of D2: LOD 1.11b.

3. Get DIABLO 2: LORD OF DESTRUCTION v1.11b [ENGLISH] NO-CD/FIXED EXE (1.05MB) from here ( http://www.gameburnworld.com/gp/gamefixes/diablo2lordofdestruction.shtml )

4. Extract the rar, and you will get a file that is 2.03 MB large, named simply "Game".

5. Back up the existing "Game" file, located in your Diablo 2 directory, then replace it with the crack.

Congratulations, you now have a cracked version of D2: LOD 1.11b.
